      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to own a true masterpiece! This vehicle is in flawless, showroom condition, looking and performing exactly as it did when it first debuted. It has been cared for with the utmost precision, making it a rare find for any enthusiast seeking perfection.",
      "price": 49900.0,
